title: Mamae Natureza
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Buffet, Salad bar, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Uses organic and locally produced ingredients. Vegan options are the self service buffet. Part of the earnings is directed to the Sao Carlos Environmental Protection Association, the NGO which manages the restaurant, and for distribution to the employees.
